Class AppointmentOutcomeService

java.lang.Object
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.entity.AppointmentOutcomeService
public class AppointmentOutcomeService extends Object
Service class for managing appointment outcome records. Provides functionality to view, update, and retrieve appointment outcome records.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    AppointmentOutcomeService()
    Constructs an AppointmentOutcomeService and initializes the appointment outcome records by loading them using AppointmentOutcomeRecordsDataLoader.

    • AppointmentOutcomeService

      public AppointmentOutcomeService()
      Constructs an AppointmentOutcomeService and initializes the appointment outcome records by loading them using AppointmentOutcomeRecordsDataLoader.

  • Method Details

    • viewAppointmentOutComeRecord

      public void viewAppointmentOutComeRecord()
      Displays all appointment outcome records. If no records are available, a message is displayed.

    • viewPendingAppointmentOutcomeRecords

      public void viewPendingAppointmentOutcomeRecords()
      Displays only the pending appointment outcome records. If no pending records exist, a clearance message is displayed.

    • updatePrescriptionStatus

      public boolean updatePrescriptionStatus(String recordID, String newStatus)
      Updates the prescribed status of an appointment outcome record with the specified record ID. The record is also updated in the underlying data source.
      Parameters:
      recordID - the ID of the record to be updated.
      newStatus - the new status to set for the prescription.
      Returns:
      true if the record was successfully updated, false otherwise.

    • getAllAppointmentOutcomeRecords

      public List<AppointmentOutcomeRecord> getAllAppointmentOutcomeRecords()
      Retrieves all appointment outcome records.
      Returns:
      a list of all appointment outcome records.

    • getPendingAppointmentOutcomeRecords

      public List<AppointmentOutcomeRecord> getPendingAppointmentOutcomeRecords()
      Retrieves only the pending appointment outcome records, identified by their prescribed status being "Pending".
      Returns:
      a list of pending appointment outcome records.
